    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>French Renaissance shawms with a wind cap, six single fingerholes, one double fingerhole, and one rear thumbhole.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
